<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.2.2">
<l>kaṇṭōṅ kaṇṭōṅ kaṇṭōṅ kaṇṇuk kiṉiyaṉa kaṇṭōm</l>
<l>toṇṭī rellīrum vārīr toḻutu toḻutuniṉ ṟārttum</l>
<l>vaṇṭār taṇṇantu ḻāyāṉ mātavaṉ pūtaṅkaṇ maṇmēl</l>
<l>paṇṭāṉ pāṭiniṉ ṟāṭip parantu tirikiṉ ṟaṉavē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>We have seen, we have seen, we have seen. Thingssweet to the eyes we have seen.</l>
<l>Devotees, you all come! We will shout, constantly worshipping [and] worshipping.</l>
<l>The bhūtas of the one with cool tulsi on which bees hum, Mādava, they roam</l>
<l>widely on earth, singing melodies, constantly dancing.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
